data.value: Keeping in view the challenging roles and practical concepts of coding, problem solving and logic building we have designed this Toll plaza app to transform the manual and time taking process intoa faster and digitized one. It consists of a complete reusable code covering all the required components which serves all the basic requirements of Toll plaza.

data.name: label9.Text
